sentence: Private Eye parodied Sue Townsend ' s The Secret Diary of Adrian Mole, age 13 ¾ to write The Secret Diary of John Major, age 47 ¾, in which Major was portrayed as naïve and childish, keeping lists of his enemies in a Rymans Notebook called his Bastards Book, and featuring my wife Norman and Mr Dr Mawhinney as recurring character s.
